      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 피어코드명조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-QJLZ005-CALL-RTN.

      *@1.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJLZ005-IN

      *@1.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드                                               01860024
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD                                       01870024
             TO XQJLZ005-I-GROUP-CO-CD                                  01880024
      *@   기준년월                                                   01940024
           MOVE XDJL4017-I-BASE-YMD(1:6)                                01950024
             TO XQJLZ005-I-BASE-YM                                      01960024
      *@   피어코드                                                   01940024
           MOVE XDJL4017-I-PEER-DSTCD                                   01950024
             TO XQJLZ005-I-TE-PEER-DSTCD                                01960024

      *@1.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJLZ005 XQJLZ005-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    MOVE SPACE
                      TO XQJLZ005-O-PEER-CD-NAME
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   피어코드명                                                 02660024
           MOVE XQJLZ005-O-PEER-CD-NAME                                 02670024
             TO XDJL4017-O-PEER-CD-NAME                                 02680024
           .
       S3100-QJLZ005-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 피어코드별TE현황조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3200-QJL0171-CALL-RTN.

      *@2.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL0171-IN

      *@2.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드                                               01860024
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD                                       01870024
             TO XQJL0171-I-GROUP-CO-CD                                  01880024
      *@   기준년월일                                                 01940024
           MOVE XDJL4017-I-BASE-YMD                                     01950024
             TO XQJL0171-I-BASE-YMD                                     01960024
      *@   피어코드
           IF XDJL4017-I-PEER-DSTCD = SPACE
               MOVE ALL '%'
                 TO XQJL0171-I-TE-PEER-DSTCD
           ELSE
               MOVE XDJL4017-I-PEER-DSTCD                               01950024
                 TO XQJL0171-I-TE-PEER-DSTCD
           END-IF
191220*@   국내외구분코드                                             01940024
           MOVE XDJL4017-I-HMAB-DSTCD                                   01950024
             TO XQJL0171-I-HMAB-DSTCD                                   01960024

      *@2.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL0171 XQJL0171-CA

      *@2.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@2.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   합계처리로인해　추출건수가　１보다　클때　출력
           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > 1
      *@   출력건수                                                   02660024
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT                                        02670024
             TO XDJL4017-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1                              02680024
           ELSE
           MOVE ZERO
             TO XDJL4017-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
           END-IF

      *@   OUTPUT 출력
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1                             02730024
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4017-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1                    02740024
      *@       피어구분
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-TE-PEER-DSTCD(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-PEER-DSTCD1(WK-I)
      *@       피어코드명
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-PEER-CD-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-PEER-CD-NAME1(WK-I)
      *@       대상업체건수
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-TAGET-ENTP-NOITM(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-TAGET-ENTP-NOITM1(WK-I)
      *@       명목액기준한도
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM1(WK-I)
      *@       명목액기준잔액
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL1(WK-I)
      *@       TE한도환산금액
               MOVE XQJL0171-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4017-O-TE-LIMT-AUC1(WK-I)
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3200-QJL0171-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
